---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { jewelryReview, business } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Selling Jewelry | Easton Rare Coin & Precious Metals"
  description="Sell gold jewelry in a private, professional setting at Easton Rare Coin & Precious Metals in Easton, PA."
>
  <section class="page-hero container narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">Selling jewelry</p>
    <h1>Turn unwanted gold jewelry into cash with a transparent, no-pressure process.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The original page focused on simplicity, clarity, and strong payouts. Those points
      stay here, but with a better reading experience and stronger trust presentation.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container two-column">
      <div class="prose-card">
        <h2>What stays from the original content</h2>
        <p>
          Clients can bring in old or unused jewelry for a precise evaluation. The shop
          explains value clearly, works in a secure office environment, and makes it easy
          to decide whether to sell.
        </p>
        <p>
          When gold prices are strong, even a small amount of jewelry can produce a
          meaningful payout. That message is worth keeping, but it should be framed with
          confidence instead of repeated promotional text.
        </p>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="quote-card">
        <p>"{jewelryReview}"</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt-section">
    <div class="container process-grid">
      <article class="process-card">
        <span class="process-number">01</span>
        <h2>Bring in your jewelry</h2>
        <p>Gold, silver, gemstone, and unwanted pieces are all reviewed item by item.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="process-card">
        <span class="process-number">02</span>
        <h2>Receive a clear appraisal</h2>
        <p>The valuation is explained transparently so you understand the offer.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="process-card">
        <span class="process-number">03</span>
        <h2>Choose whether to sell</h2>
        <p>No-pressure offers and no charge for in-store appraisals.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split-highlight">
      <div class="contact-panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Ready to sell?</p>
        <h2>Call ahead or walk in.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-panel muted">
        <p><a href={business.phoneHref}>{business.phoneDisplay}</a></p>
        <p><a href={business.emailHref}>{business.email}</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
